<h2>Other Metadata Services</h2>
<br>
<p>The Metadata Team oversees the descriptive metadata that facilitates the discovery, identification, evaluation, and selection of the UCLA Library's online resources. In addition, the Team also serves as a resource for other UCLA units on metadata for online resources.</p>

